snippet.title: CELEBRITY AND NARCISSISM - #narcissist #celebrity #JustinBieber #AmberHeard
snippet.description:
Celebrity life for me as a kid was a huge escape. I chased many the autographs when I was a young one. Join me as I explore how celebrities use an image to control their fans and the public in general.
